---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="PeptideRundown privacy policy covering analytics, email contact, cookies, and third-party services."
>
  <section class="bg-surface py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-primary mb-3">Privacy</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-text mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate max-w-none">
        <p>PeptideRundown collects limited information needed to operate the site, understand traffic, and respond to messages.</p>
        <h2>Analytics</h2>
        <p>We use analytics tools, including Google Analytics, to understand aggregate traffic patterns and improve the site. These tools may use cookies or similar technologies.</p>
        <h2>Email</h2>
        <p>If you contact us by email, we will use the information you provide to respond to your request. Do not send private medical information.</p>
        <h2>Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p>PeptideRundown links to external resources such as PubMed, regulatory sites, and related projects. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of external websites.</p>
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions about this policy can be sent to <a href="mailto:hello@peptiderundown.com">hello@peptiderundown.com</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
